Title: Local logit regression for recovery rate
Author-Name: Nithi Sopitpongstorn
Author-X-Name-First: Nithi 
Author-X-Name-Last: Sopitpongstorn
Author-Email: nithi.sopitpongstorn@monash.edu
Author-Name: Param Silvapulle
Author-X-Name-First: Param
