Title: Kernel-based inference in time-varying coefficient models with multiple integrated regressors
Author-Name: Degui Li
Author-X-Name-First: Degui
Author-X-Name-Last: Li
Author-Email: degui.li@york.ac.uk 
Author-Name: Peter CB Phillips
Author-X-Name-First: Peter
